## Project Structure

This is a multi-module Maven project using TeaVM Lambda for full-stack Java development.

### Modules

- **{{APP_NAME}}-common** — Shared models and interfaces
- **{{APP_NAME}}-api** — Backend API service (compiles to JavaScript via TeaVM, runs on Cloud Run)
{{#FRONTEND}}
- **{{APP_NAME}}-frontend** — Frontend SPA (compiles to JavaScript via TeaVM React)
{{/FRONTEND}}

## Building

```bash
./mvnw clean package        # Build all modules
./mvnw -pl {{APP_NAME}}-api package -Pteavm    # Build API with TeaVM profile
./mvnw -pl {{APP_NAME}}-api package -Pjvm      # Build API with JVM profile
```

## Local Development

```bash
./setup-local.sh             # First-time setup (starts Docker services)
./dev.sh                     # Start local dev environment
```

## Testing

```bash
cd {{APP_NAME}}-api && ./run-tests.sh    # Run API tests
```

