## API Patterns

- Resources use `@Path`, `@GET`, `@POST`, etc. annotations
- Dependency injection via `@Component`, `@Singleton`, `@Inject`
- Security via `@PermitAll` or `@RolesAllowed`
- Constructor injection is preferred
- Response objects: `Response.ok(body)`, `Response.status(code).entity(body)`
